Introduction

CocaNButter is a South Korean dance group under MLD Entertainment. They consist of 6 members: Ri.hey, ZSun, Gaga, Bicki, Jillin and Beebi. They were formed in 2018 and officially debuted as a music group with their 1st single album called “Mi Deh Yah“, on October 6, 2022 with the line up: Ri.hey, ZSun, Gaga and Bicki. They were contestants on “Street Woman Fighter“.
